title: JS Carr - The Devil in Robes or Sin of Priests.pdf
description:
THE DEVIL IN ROBES, OR THE SIN OF PRIESTS

Homes of Cuba, Puerto Rico and the Philippine Islands united, and the baleful influences of Romanism forever removed from wives and daughters.

TRUTHS THAT SHOCK THE CIVILIZED WORLD.
Every Page a Story of Ungodly Acts of the Priest-Craft and Upheld by their Superiors.

Compiled from facts told by eye-witnesses, which includes soldier and
civilian, who have given their lives to liberate the unhappy natives of these
Islands, and rebuke abhorrent Catholicism.

INTRODUCTORY BY: REV. J. SCOTT CARR, D. D.,
